--- PROJECT SWERVE CONFIGURATION ---

1. Mapbox Configuration

Used for the 60 FPS WebGL rendering engine

REACT_APP_MAPBOX_TOKEN=your_mapbox_token_here
MAPBOX_STYLE=mapbox://styles/mapbox/dark-v11

2. Tomorrow.io Weather API Configuration

Used for hyper-local, minute-by-minute weather data

REACT_APP_TOMORROW_TOKEN=your_tomorrow_token_here

3. TomTom Traffic API Configuration

Used for real-time traffic incident detection (crashes/hazards)

REACT_APP_TOMTOM_TOKEN=your_tomtom_token_here

4. Road511 Camera API Configuration

Used for universal highway camera snapshots

REACT_APP_ROAD511_TOKEN=your_road511_token_here

5. OpenWeatherMap Precipitation Radar

Used for live precipitation radar tile overlay

REACT_APP_OWM_KEY=your_openweathermap_api_key_here

Server Configuration

PORT=3000